        public <EXCEPTION extends Throwable> void assertHealthy​(Class<EXCEPTION> panicDisguise)
                                                 throws EXCEPTION extends Throwable
        Asserts that the database is in good health. If that is not the case then the cause of the unhealthy state is wrapped in an exception of the given type, i.e. the panic disguise.
